  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Support to ActionAid Palestine&apos;s fundraising</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">ActionAid UK&apos;s has a partnership with People&apos;s Postocde Lottery and benefits directly from lottery draws assigned within a calendar year. This PPL funding will bolster fundraising, policy and advocacy work in Palestine, particularly in the context of fast-changing, volatile political and security situation in Gaza and West Bank, which demands quick response from AAP to keep momentum and raise awareness of the needs particularly to the global/donor communities. By doing so, AAP will be able to present a compelling case for global/donor communities to release funding for Palestine.</narrative>
  </description>
